<br>
She had this...icky feeling around Ares.  And he wouldn't go away.  She felt as though at any moment something bad were going to happen.  Anytime he was around she felt tense.  Without knowing how, or why, she felt as if he were constantly degrading her while building her up at the same time.<br>
<br>
She wandered until she stood in the middle of the village nearing tears.  She didn't want to bother her Queen with a little girl's problem.  Who would she go to?<br>
<br>
She stood there, looking from hut to hut, wondering who she could talk to that could help.</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uqueenhera.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Queen Hera</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Queen of the Gods</span><br>  Posts: 27<br> <font color=#993300>(3/19/01 3:48:43 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> a little help</span><hr size=1> :::Suddenly, a voice spoke to Nicodema from behind.  Hera had appeared quietly, no cry of peacocks or flash of lightening.  Even the winter was getting to the Queen of the Gods:::<br>
<br>
Does my son trouble you, dear Amazon? :::She wore a black cloak decorated in peacock feathers.  Her head was covered by the cloak's black fur that warmed her cheeks.   Bits of wavy auburn tendrils flowed from underneath the hood.  Upon her face was warm smile.::: <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=nicodemaalcinoe>Nicodema Alcinoe</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Amazon Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 32<br> <font color=#993300>(3/22/01 2:57:19 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/xnicodemax/images/nicodmea.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: a little help</span><hr size=1> ::She whipped around, caught off guard.  She shivered inside the fur cloak, not only from the cold, but from being spoken directly to by the awesome Goddess.::<br>
<br>
Y-yes ma'am.  I'm afraid I don't understand what he wants of me.  He says he wants to help me:  to make me into a better warrior.  But each time he's around I get the feeling that he's there to make fun of me and treat me like a child.<br>
<br>
::She bites her lip::  Please, may I trouble you for some advice, your highness? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uqueenhera.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Queen Hera</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Queen of the Gods</span><br>  Posts: 29<br> <font color=#993300>(3/28/01 6:23:05 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> troubled amazon</span><hr size=1> Hera quietly listened as Nicodema spoke to her of her son, Ares.  She had known that her son of war had been trying to court this amazon.  Much like he had any warrior women he thought he might could possibly make his queen of war...or could just use.<br>
&quot;First, let us to a warmer place,&quot; Hera smiled. &quot;For I care not for this frozen air.  Shall we?&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> Melousa</span><br> <span class=usertitle>Unregistered User</span><br>   <font color=#993300>(3/31/01 10:36:40 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> ~stops, hearing Hera and the othre amazon ~</span><hr size=1> ~ Feeling quite alone, Melousa walks through the snow, her extended belly a bit bigger, she wraps her furs around her tightly, enjoying the cold air, her heart empty, she feels more alone now then ever before, hearing Hera's voice she stops, not wanting to evesdrop, but she doesnt know what else to do, she hears the other Amazon talk of Ares and how he is trying to court her, she looks down to her belly, tears welling in her eyes, knowing that she was stupid to trust a him of all gods, a bit pissed she hasnt heard or seen him since he planted his seed in her, she sighs and turns walking away slowly in the other direction~ <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=nicodemaalcinoe>Nicodema Alcinoe</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Amazon Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 33<br> <font color=#993300>(4/4/01 3:10:48 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> ::agrees::</span><hr size=1> ::Nods:: Of course, as you wish.  Do you have somewhere in mind? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uposeidonkofc.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Poseidonkofc</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 24<br> <font color=#993300>(5/19/01 9:19:19 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: </span><hr size=1> ::Looking down from Olympus Poseidon looks at Hera and the amazon. Poseidon appears by Hera's side invisible to the amazon. He looks to the amazon and then to Hera. Being heard only by Hera Poseidon speaks.::<br>
<br>
&quot;My sister, leave these mortals alone. If your son wants to court this woman let him. What right has she to blame a god for her troubles or sorrows?&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uqueenhera.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Queen Hera</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Queen of the Gods</span><br>  Posts: 67<br> <font color=#993300>(6/4/01 3:17:28 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> A tavern</span><hr size=1> Hera leads the amazon into a warm tavern.  She appears disquised to the other mortals as they walk in.  Then frowns upon hearing her brother.  She sends him a message.  ~*Stay out of this.  If she wishes not to be w/ my son.  Then her wish should be respected.*~<br>
They walk to a table near the fire and sit down. Hera turns her eyes to Nico and smiles gently. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uposeidonkofc.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Poseidonkofc</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 57<br> <font color=#993300>(6/5/01 4:22:25 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re::</span><hr size=1> ::The great God Poseidon heeds his sisters words and respctfully backs away and fades.:: <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uposeidonkofc.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Poseidonkofc</A> at: 6/14/01 9:51:21 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/unicodema.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Nicodema</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#993300>(7/2/01 12:17:58 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Fending off Ares</span><hr size=1> ((OOC:  I apologize PROFUSELY for the absence...for some reason I couldn't get my logon to work and had to make a new one.  I'm SO SORRY...thanks. - Nico mun))<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  Sitting across from the goddess, Nico pulled off her leather gloves.<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> <br>
<br>
I don't mean disrespect to him.  But, well, I'm not sure of his motives.  He says he wants only to train me.  Yet, I've heard rumors of his...well...philandering.  ::Blushes::  Maybe that's a bad word, but...I can think of no other that fits.  You know him well:  can he be </i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/unicodema.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Nicodema</A> at: 7/2/01 12:20:30 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uqueenhera.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Queen Hera</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Bronze Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 104<br> <font color=#993300>(7/2/01 3:38:49 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Ares</span><hr size=1> &quot;Well, the leaf does not fall far from the tree, Nicodema.  Ares is very much like his father,&quot; Hera sighed as she spoke, her eyes seeming to darken and then move back to their icy blue.  &quot;I know his attentions do not stay to one woman for very long.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uxgoddessaphrodite.showPublicProfile?language=EN>xGoddess Aphrodite</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 49<br> <font color=#993300>(7/2/01 6:49:03 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Ease-dropping</span><hr size=1> ::High on Mt. Olympus, Aphrodite works her way to Zeus' reflecting pool.::    &quot;Zeus won't mind if I use this....besides, he's too busy with the titaness Maia to even know I'm taking a peek.&quot;<br>
<br>
::She looks in the pool and admires her reflection. She fixes her hair and blows herself a kiss. Then she waves her hand over the pool and observes the conversation between Hera and the Amazon.::<br>
<br>
&quot;This sounds like Ares up to his ways again...I wonder if she's gonna bite?&quot;  ::Curiosity gets the best of her (especially when it come to Ares and lust) and she disappears off of Olympus.  She reappears outside the tavern.  She disguises herself as a barmaid and trots non-chalantly into the tavern::: <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/unicodema.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Nicodema</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#993300>(7/3/01 2:20:42 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Publicly Proclaiming her Vows</span><hr size=1> ::Nico nodded.  She had recently discovered the god's ways::<br>
<br>
I have no intentions of ever sleeping with a man, Mother Goddess.  Ever.  And that is where things appear clouded for me.  I would never, ever...even if he is the mighty Ares.  I have taken a vow of celibacy.  I am very devote to this vow.  It helps me concentrate on what is important: being a servant to the goddesses and my sisters.  But, how will Ares take this?  Is it blasphemy for me to...well, reject him?  I wish to remain an everlasting servant to the gods.  But what kind of god asks this of his followers?<br>
<br>
::The young girl was truly confused, her faith shaken.:: <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uqueenhera.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Queen Hera</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Bronze Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 106<br> <font color=#993300>(7/3/01 5:22:45 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> a vow</span><hr size=1> &quot;Nicodema, Ares should understand your vow...tho I know he will continue to pursue until his lust is driven else where,&quot; Hera answered and then felt an odd sensation of familiarity.  She glanced around the room quickly and not seeing anyone she knew, she shrugged it off as it was not a bad feeling.<br>
&quot;You have the right to your vows and no God should push it.  Mayhaps you should speak to Hestia on this, for she knows how hard it is to be a virgin with pursuers.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uxgoddessaphrodite.showPublicProfile?language=EN>xGoddess Aphrodite</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 52<br> <font color=#993300>(7/3/01 11:18:13 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Takes a seat</span><hr size=1> ::she takes a seat at a nearby table so she can ease-drop better.  As she listens, she finds out the amazon will not have anything to do with Ares.  This puts a downer on her evening.::<br>
<br>
&quot;What a bummer!  Just when I thought this evening was gonna get good...&quot;<br>
<br>
::A drunken warlord moves in on Aphrodite/barmaid and clumsily put an arm around her::  &quot;I can help you have a good evening, H~hiccup~Honey! &quot;<br>
<br>
::Aphrodite smirks and shoos the ale-reaking fool away.  She put her elbow on the table. She rests her head on her hand and sighs:: <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uxgoddessaphrodite.showPublicProfile?language=EN>xGoddess Aphrodite</A> at: 7/7/01 11:08:21 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/unicodema.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Nicodema</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 3<br> <font color=#993300>(7/4/01 7:09:46 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Takes a seat</span><hr size=1> ::Nods to Hera with a smile::  I would like to speak with her.  ::Sighs, relieved::  So, I am not being unreasonable?  Informing Ares that his efforts are futile wouldn't be wrong?  I respect him, but as a warrior and a god.  I have no desire to anger him, but I have no desire...well, for anything else,either.  I just want to be a good warrior and an asset to my sisters. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uxgoddessaphrodite.showPublicProfile?language=EN>xGoddess Aphrodite</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 68<br> <font color=#993300>(7/9/01 8:16:28 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.xenafan.com/gallery/official/aphrodite_02.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Major bummer...</span><hr size=1> ::Looks from the amazon to Hera and sighs.  She gets up from her seat and begins to walk out of the temple.  But before she gets any futher, a rowdy group of warlord (including the one she dissed before) stop her in her tracks.  They begin to taunt her.  She mumbles to them to get out of her way as silent as possible as to not draw any attention to herself.  Unfortunately the warlords don't understand greek to well and really gets on her case:: <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showMessage?topicID=247.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.showMessage?topicID=244.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.emailToFriend?topicID=178.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.threadControl?topicID=178.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=178.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=178.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub11.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="amazonsuniteamazonsunitescrollboard">Amazons Unite Scroll Board<option value="amazonsunitefrm37">The Mythical Odyssey Forum<option value="amazonsunitefrm23">The Olympian Gods<option value="amazonsunitefrm15">Black Sea Tavern and Inn<option value="amazonsunitefrm32">The Mythical Odyssey<option value="amazonsunitefrm35">Amazon Nation Alliance